# Mobile Shop Automation Testing

This project automates testing of the mobile phone section on [anhoch.mk](https://www.anhoch.mk) using Selenium WebDriver with C# and NUnit. It covers features such as search, brand filtering, and adding to cart.

## ğŸ§ª Project Objective
To verify that key functionalities like search, filtering by brand, and adding to the cart work correctly through automated tests.

## ğŸ“Œ Scope

### âœ… What will be tested:
- **Search Functionality** â€” Searching phones by model/brand.
- **Filtering by Brand** â€” Only phones of selected brand are shown.
- **Add to Cart** â€” Products correctly added to shopping cart.
- **Product Details** â€” Info like price/specs shown correctly.
- **Mobile Responsiveness** â€” UI works well on all screen sizes.

### âŒ What will NOT be tested:
- Payment Gateway
- User Login/Register
- External Services
- Non-Mobile categories

