## ğŸ§± Automation Details

- **Framework:** Selenium WebDriver + C#
- **Test Runner:** NUnit
- **Pattern:** Page Object Model (POM)
- **CI/CD:** Azure DevOps Pipelines
- **Browser:** Google Chrome (via ChromeDriver)

## ğŸ“Š Results & Reporting
- Tests run via NUnit
